title: Toddler Girls' Shanel Fisherman Sandals - Cat & Jack™

bullet_descriptions: Care and Cleaning: Care Instructions Not Provided
Features: Quarter Strap, Hook and Loop Closure, Open Toe
description.downstream_description: She'll be ready for fun in the sun whenever she sports the Shanel Fisherman Sandals from Cat & Jack™. These strappy sandals feature an open design to keep her feet cool and comfy on warm, sunny days, and they're easy to dress up or down thanks to the classic straps of the fisherman-style design. A back sling strap helps provide a firm fit that stays put on her feet as she moves, while the buckle accent conceals a hook-and-loop fastener that makes for adjustable wear as well as making on and off easy.
description.soft_bullet_description:
•Strappy toddler sandals are great for everyday wear or dressy occasions
•Multiple straps help make sure her shoes stay put on her feet
•Adjustable ankle strap lets her find a comfortable fit
•Buckle accent conceals a hook-and-loop closure for easy on and off
